{"tid":142591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港應該仿傚《楢山節考》優良文化","createTime":"2017-03-04T02:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T03:59:24.000Z","uid":55851,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"416046f093f289643932688d9350d2c169e73f77","tid":142591,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://whenidream.files.wordpress.com/2009/10/e6a5a2e5b1b1e7af80e880831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhenidream.files.wordpress.com%2F2009%2F10%2Fe6a5a2e5b1b1e7af80e880831.jpg&h=458910ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《楢山節考》中，老人一到七十歲便由長子背負上山，留在山上。先輩會得到山神的祝福，安樂無憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六十五歲及以上長者的比例推算將由二零一四年的15%顯著上升至二零六四年的36%</span></strong>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n送晒班廢老上山就可以一次過解決晒長生津＋生果金＋全民退保＋醫院床位不足＋公立診症輪候時間過長＋安老院舍不足＋關愛座＋城市衛生＋藍絲＋建制票倉＋房屋不足問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b77e8058529d4e4ee90821b1751818a486f890","tid":142591,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1146688733c260c579f8a82aea0260710d1c6ba4","tid":142591,"uid":20943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"驚班廢老喺上面大逃殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n篩到得返一個超級廢老 落山搵我哋尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ff44eeb5b14ab7b34564f8f9b8192f5cd31206","tid":142591,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"19才子:楢山節考模式送晒上大亞灣"},{"pid":"0b1a12b8c6ddc52444c6906e6bf620fbe930dd34","tid":142591,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19才子:楢山節考模式送晒上大亞灣</blockquote><br />\n係大亞灣起老人園~"},{"pid":"5f11d3d6305de88c142f7bf76561330b3bd02fa0","tid":142591,"uid":61